<section id="contacto" class="py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="grid gap-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/45 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] lg:p-10">
        <div>
            <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-yellow">Contacto</p>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">Cuéntame qué quieres construir.</h2>
            <p class="mt-6 max-w-md text-lg leading-8 text-zinc-400">
                Si tienes una idea, una web que mejorar o un producto que lanzar, puedo convertirlo en una experiencia clara, moderna y rápida.
            </p>
        </div>
        <form action="mailto:manuelnavarrohigueras@gmail.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain" class="grid gap-6">
            <div>
                <label for="name" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-zinc-400">Nombre</label>
                <input id="name" name="name" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-950/60 px-5 py-4 text-white outline-none transition duration-200 placeholder:text-zinc-600 focus:border-yellow focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow/30" placeholder="Tu nombre" autocomplete="name">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="email" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-zinc-400">Email</label>
                <input id="email" name="email" type="email" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-950/60 px-5 py-4 text-white outline-none transition duration-200 placeholder:text-zinc-600 focus:border-yellow focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow/30" placeholder="tu@email.com" autocomplete="email">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="message" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-zinc-400">Mensaje</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" class="w-full resize-none rounded-2xl border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-950/60 px-5 py-4 text-white outline-none transition duration-200 placeholder:text-zinc-600 focus:border-yellow focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow/30" placeholder="Háblame de tu proyecto"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button class="inline-flex w-fit items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-yellow px-7 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-white focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-yellow focus-visible:ring-offset-4 focus-visible:ring-offset-zinc-950">
                Enviar mensaje
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>
